 upon himself to steal it in order to protect it. And he does but Abigail Chase the curator of the National Archives, where it is kept, discovers what he has done and tries to stop him but gets caught in the crossfire between Ben and Ian, so Ben takes her with him. While she doesdn\'t believe him, he is determined to prove he is right about the treasure. But it won\'t be easy cause Ian\'s always a step behind him and he is being hunted by the FBI.\r\n-\r\nrcs0411@yahoo.com\r\n\r\nSince childhood, Benjamin Franklin Gates has known that he is decended from a long line of people whose job is to guard a treasure hidden by the Founding Fathers, who hid clues to its whereabouts in the country\'s currency and on the back of the Declaration of Independence. Now, he has learned of a plot to steal the Declaration, and has only one option: steal it himself. Even if he pulls off this monumental task, keeping the treasure safe is still going to be incredibly hard, especially since the FBI has also gotten wind of the scheme.\r\n-\r\nrmlohner','Blu-ray',1,1,'',0,'2020-04-30','','2020-04-08 12:23:06','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H8PwAQsV63E','','','','',0,0,0,'Argentina::Atp\r\nAustralia::PG\r\nBrazil::Livre\r\nCanada::G\r\nChile::TE\r\nDenmark::11\r\nFinland::K-12/9\r\nFrance::Tous publics\r\nGermany::12\r\nHong Kong::IIA\r\nIceland::L\r\nIndia::U\r\nIreland::PG\r\nItaly::T\r\nJapan::G\r\nMalaysia::U\r\nMexico::B\r\nNetherlands::12\r\nNew Zealand::PG\r\nNorway::11\r\nPeru::Apt\r\nPhilippines::G\r\nPoland::12\r\nPortugal::M/12\r\nRussia::12+\r\nSingapore::PG\r\nSouth Africa::PG\r\nSouth Korea::12\r\nSpain::A\r\nSweden::7\r\nSwitzerland::12\r\nTaiwan::PG-12\r\nUnited Kingdom::PG\r\nUnited States::PG',0),(29,'0162222','Cast Away','Cast Away','Cast Away\r\nNáufrago\r\nCast Away - Verschollen\r\nКорабокрушенецът\r\nSeul au monde\r\n荒岛余生\r\nBrodolom života\r\nTrosečník\r\nTrosecnik\r\nManbuz\r\nKaldale uhutud\r\nCast Away - Tuuliajolla\r\nTuuliajolla\r\nNavagos\r\nΝαυαγός\r\nSzámkiv