\nMichael of lillym_325@yahoo.com\r\n\r\nIn the clear skies of Montana, during an unprecedented worldwide incident of simultaneous first contact with extraterrestrial life forms, an ominous alien pod, out of twelve in total, comes to a standstill, hovering only a few feet over the green prairies. Inevitably, as panic ensues, Colonel G.T. Weber recruits a team of various experts, including the esteemed linguistics and dialectology, Professor Dr Louise Banks, and the theoretical physicist, Dr Ian Donnelly, burdening them with the impossible task to decipher a coded conversation with the intergalactic visitors. But, when all attempts to communicate prove fruitless, a practical, yet very important question will arise: does humanity have enough vocabulary to understand the aliens\' answer before a new global war sparks?\r\n-\r\nNick Riganas','Blu-ray',1,1,'',0,'2020-05-01','','2020-04-14 10:22:09','','','','','',0,0,0,'Argentina::13\r\nAustralia::M\r\nAustria::12\r\nBrazil::10\r\nCanada::G\r\nChile::TE+7\r\nCzechia::12\r\nDenmark::11\r\nFinland::K-12\r\nFrance::Tous publics\r\nGermany::12\r\nGreece::K-12\r\nHong Kong::IIA\r\nHungary::12\r\nIceland::12\r\nIndia::UA\r\nIndonesia::13+\r\nIreland::12\r\nItaly::T\r\nJapan::G\r\nLithuania::N-13\r\nMalaysia::P13\r\nMexico::B\r\nNetherlands::12\r\nNew Zealand::M\r\nNorway::9\r\nPhilippines::PG-13\r\nPoland::12\r\nPortugal::M/12\r\nRussia::16+\r\nSingapore::PG13\r\nSouth Africa::PG\r\nSouth Korea::12\r\nSpain::7\r\nSweden::11\r\nSwitzerland::10\r\nTaiwan::PG-12\r\nThailand::G\r\nTurkey::7+\r\nUnited Kingdom::12\r\nUnited States::PG-13\r\nUkraine::12\r\nUnited Arab Emirates::PG-15\r\nVietnam::C13',12),(118,'0472043','Apocalypto','Apocalypto','Apocalypto\r\nАпокалипто\r\nApokalipto\r\nアポカリプト\r\nАпокалипсис\r\nApokalipsis\r\n阿波卡獵逃\r\nKıyamet\r\nАпокаліпсис\r\nMel Gibson\'s Apocalypto',2006,139,7.8,304621,'Maya','United States','Action\r\nAdventure\r\nDrama\r\nThriller','Mel Gibson','Mel Gibson\r\nFarhad Safinia','Judi Bell\r\nVicki 