d to liberty is always drenched in blood.\r\n-\r\nNick Riganas\r\n\r\nIn 14th Century Scotland, William Wallace leads his people in a rebellion against the tyranny of the English King, who has given English nobility the \'Prima Nocta\' - a right to take all new brides for the first night. The Scots are none too pleased with the brutal English invaders, but they lack leadership to fight back. Wallace creates a legend of himself, with his courageous defense of his people and attacks on the English.\r\n-\r\nRob Hartill','Blu-ray',1,1,'',0,'2020-05-01','','2020-04-14 10:35:05','','','','','',0,0,1,'Argentina::16\r\nAustralia::MA\r\nBelgium::KT/EA\r\nBrazil::16\r\nCanada::13+\r\nChile::14\r\nCzechia::15\r\nDenmark::15\r\nFinland::K-15/13\r\nFrance::Tous publics\r\nGermany::16\r\nGreece::K-12\r\nHong Kong::IIB\r\nHungary::16\r\nIceland::16\r\nIndia::A\r\nIndonesia::21\r\nIreland::15\r\nItaly::T\r\nJapan::G\r\nMalaysia::18SG\r\nMexico::C\r\nNetherlands::16\r\nNew Zealand::R16\r\nNigeria::18\r\nNorway::18\r\nPeru::14\r\nPhilippines::R-18\r\nPoland::12\r\nPortugal::M/12\r\nRussia::16+\r\nSaudi Arabia::R15\r\nSingapore::M18\r\nSouth Africa::16\r\nSouth Korea::15\r\nSpain::18\r\nSweden::15\r\nTurkey::13+\r\nUnited Kingdom::15\r\nUnited States::R\r\nUnited Arab Emirates::18+',18),(130,'1823672','Chappie','Chappie','Chappie\r\nЧaпи\r\nHumandroid\r\nチャッピー\r\nRobots vārdā Čapijs\r\nČapis\r\nРобот по имени Чаппи\r\nЧапи: Робот који је променио свет\r\n成人世界\r\nРобот Чаппі\r\nChappi laqabli robot\r\nChappie: Cảnh Sát Người Máy',2015,120,6.8,244180,'English','United States','Action\r\nCrime\r\nDrama\r\nSci-Fi\r\nThriller','Neill Blomkamp','Neill Blomkamp\r\nTerri Tatchell','James Bitonti\r\nNeill Blomkamp\r\nVictoria Burkhart\r\nTrishia Downie\r\nSimon Kinberg\r\nBen Waisbren','Hans Zimmer','Sharlto Copley\r\nDev Patel\r\nNinja\r\nYo-Landi Visser\r\nJose Pablo Cantillo\r\nHugh Jackman\r\nSigourney Weaver\r\nBrandon Auret\r\nJohnny Selema\r\nAnderson Cooper\r\nMaurice Carpede\r\nJason 