 prostitute, and a pal with Tourette\'s - constantly needing an electric charge to keep going.\r\n-\r\n\r\nSome believe that, when you\'ve stared death in the face, everything after that is easy. However, after his high-octane experience in Crank (2006), the indestructible British assassin, Chev Chelios, finds himself neck-deep in trouble, and one heart short. This time, with his ticker removed and replaced with a temporary, battery-powered artificial heart, once again, Chev embarks on a frenzied quest to stay alive, on the hunt for his missing organ and Johnny Vang, a ruthless member of the Chinese Triad in Los Angeles. But, this is a race against time, and as Chelios leaves no stone unturned to find his stolen heart, he must never forget to recharge the device in his chest every so often, to keep himself going. The clock is ticking. Will Chev ever get his heart back?\r\n-\r\nNick Riganas','Blu-ray',1,0,'',0,'2020-05-01','','2020-04-14 10:39:19','','','','','',0,0,0,'Argentina::16\r\nAustralia::R18+\r\nBrazil::18\r\nCanada::16+\r\nDenmark::15\r\nFinland::K-18\r\nFrance::12\r\nGermany::16\r\nGreece::K-16\r\nHungary::18\r\nIceland::16\r\nIreland::18\r\nItaly::T\r\nJapan::R18+\r\nLithuania::N-16\r\nMalaysia::18PL\r\nMexico::C\r\nNetherlands::16\r\nNew Zealand::R18\r\nNorway::18\r\nPhilippines::R-13\r\nPoland::16\r\nRomania::I.M.-18\r\nRussia::18+\r\nSingapore::R21\r\nSouth Africa::18\r\nSouth Korea::18\r\nSpain::18\r\nSweden::15\r\nSwitzerland::18\r\nTaiwan::R-18\r\nTurkey::18+\r\nUnited Kingdom::18\r\nUnited States::R\r\nUkraine::18',16),(134,'0338526','Van Helsing','Van Helsing','Van Helsing\r\nVan Helsing: El cazador de monstruos\r\nVan Helsing - O Caçador de Monstros\r\nВан Хелсинг\r\nΒαν Χέλσινγκ\r\nKallarai Manithan\r\nवैन हेल्सिंग\r\nヴァン・ヘルシング\r\nVan Helsingas\r\nVan Helsing: Cazador de monstruos\r\nВан Хельсинг\r\n凡赫辛\r\nВан Хелсінг\r\nВан Хельсінг\r\nВан Гельсінг',2004,131,6.1,258632,'English\r\nLatin','United States\r\nCzech Republic','Action\r\nAdventure\r\