ask of the campus mascot - a baby. Tree immediately wakes up in the same way she had previously - in Carter\'s bed - and is unnerved to find the previous day\'s events repeating themselves. Baffled, she nonetheless relives the day and uses this second chance to avoid the tunnel and reach the party. However, the masked killer follows her to the party and murders her again. Tree again wakes up in Carter\'s bed, realizes that she is in a time loop and barricades herself in her sorority house room to avoid death. The killer, however, is already hiding there and slays her a third time..','Blu-ray',1,1,'',0,'2020-05-01','','2020-04-14 10:43:10','','','','','',0,0,0,'Argentina::13\r\nAustralia::M\r\nAustria::12\r\nBrazil::14\r\nCanada::14+\r\nChile::14\r\nColombia::15\r\nDenmark::15\r\nFinland::K-16\r\nFrance::12\r\nGermany::12\r\nHong Kong::IIB\r\nHungary::16\r\nIceland::16\r\nIndia::UA\r\nIndonesia::17+\r\nIreland::15A\r\nItaly::T\r\nJapan::G\r\nLithuania::N-16\r\nLuxembourg::16\r\nMalaysia::18\r\nMexico::B15\r\nNetherlands::16\r\nNew Zealand::M\r\nNorway::15\r\nPhilippines::R-13\r\nPoland::18\r\nPortugal::M/14\r\nRussia::16+\r\nSingapore::PG13\r\nSouth Africa::13\r\nSouth Korea::15\r\nSpain::12\r\nSweden::15\r\nSwitzerland::14\r\nTaiwan::R-12\r\nThailand::15\r\nTurkey::13+\r\nUnited Kingdom::15\r\nUnited States::PG-13\r\nUkraine::16\r\nUnited Arab Emirates::18+\r\nVietnam::C16',12),(137,'1853728','Django Unchained','Django Unchained','Django Unchained\r\nDjango sin cadenas\r\nZencirsiz Canqo\r\nDjango Livre\r\nДжанго без окови\r\nDjango déchaîné\r\n被解救的姜戈\r\nOdbjegli Django\r\nNespoutaný Django\r\nVabastatud Django\r\nDjango, o timoros\r\nDjango, ο τιμωρός\r\n黑殺令\r\nDjango elszabadul\r\nJango-ye raha shode\r\nDjango Lelo Ma\'atzorim\r\nDjango Tsunagarezaru Mono\r\nジャンゴ　繋がれざる者\r\nAtsvabinātais Džango\r\nIštrūkęs Džango\r\nDjango\r\nDjango Libertado\r\nDjango dezlănțuit\r\nДжанго освобожденный\r\nЂангова освета\r\nDivoký Django\r\nDjango brez okovov\r\nDjango desencadenad