ney travels with his partner Lee Christmas in their plane to Vilena to meet their local contact, Sandra. They have an incident with one troop and they flee from the island, but Sandra refuses to leave her country and is left behind. They investigate and discover that Church is actually from CIA, that wants them to do the dirty work to destroy the powerful drug dealer and rogue FBI agent James Munroe, who is using the island to grow coke. But Barney also feels divided between staying safe in USA or risky his life to save Sandra and his own soul.\r\n-\r\nClaudio Carvalho, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil','Blu-ray',1,1,'',0,'2020-05-01','','2020-04-14 10:46:12','','','','','',0,0,0,'Argentina::16\r\nAustralia::MA15+\r\nAustria::16\r\nBrazil::16\r\nCanada::13+\r\nDenmark::15\r\nFinland::K-16\r\nFrance::12\r\nGermany::16\r\nHong Kong::IIB\r\nHungary::16\r\nIndia::A\r\nIreland::15\r\nItaly::T\r\nJapan::R15+\r\nLithuania::N-16\r\nMalaysia::18\r\nMexico::B15\r\nNetherlands::16\r\nNew Zealand::R16\r\nNorway::15\r\nPhilippines::PG-13\r\nPoland::16\r\nPortugal::M/16\r\nRomania::I.M.-18\r\nRussia::18+\r\nSingapore::PG13\r\nSouth Korea::15\r\nSpain::16\r\nSweden::15\r\nTurkey::15+\r\nUnited Kingdom::15\r\nUnited States::R\r\nUnited Arab Emirates::PG-15',18),(141,'2322441','Fifty Shades of Grey','Fifty Shades of Grey','Fifty Shades of Grey\r\nPesëdhjetë hijet e Greit\r\nCincuenta sombras de Grey\r\nCinquenta Tons de Cinza\r\nПетдесет нюанса сиво\r\nCinquante nuances de Grey\r\nPedeset nijansi sive\r\nPadesát odstínů šedi\r\nFifty Shades of Grey Geheimes Verlangen\r\nFifty Shades Of Grey\r\nPeninta apohroseis tou gri\r\nΠενήντα αποχρώσεις του γκρι\r\nA szürke ötven árnyalata\r\nKhamishim gvanim shel afor\r\nCinquanta sfumature di grigio\r\nフィフティ・シェイズ・オブ・グレイ\r\nGreja piecdesmit nokrāsas\r\nPenkiasdesimt pilku atspalviu\r\n50 Sombras de Grey\r\nPięćdziesiąt twarzy Greya\r\nAs Cinquenta Sombras de Grey\r\n50 de umbre ale lui Grey\r\nCincizeci de umbre ale lui Grey\r\nПятьдесят оттенков серого