e late-night incident robs Grey of his happiness, leaving him an empty quadriplegic. Now, the reclusive tech mogul, Eron Keen, comes up with an offer, promising Trace to bridge the painful gap between his unresponsive limbs and his brain with the aid of his latest, state-of-the-art invention: the powerful Stem microchip. But, what if the cure is worse than the disease?\r\n-\r\nNick Riganas','Blu-ray',1,1,'',0,'2020-05-01','','2020-04-15 15:28:11','','','','','',0,0,0,'Argentina::16\r\nAustralia::MA15+\r\nBrazil::16\r\nCanada::13+\r\nColombia::15\r\nDenmark::15\r\nFinland::K-16\r\nFrance::12\r\nGermany::16\r\nGreece::K-16\r\nHong Kong::IIB\r\nIndia::18\r\nIreland::16\r\nItaly::T\r\nJapan::PG12\r\nMexico::B15\r\nNetherlands::16\r\nNew Zealand::R16\r\nNorway::15\r\nPhilippines::R-16\r\nPoland::16\r\nRussia::18+\r\nSingapore::NC16\r\nSouth Africa::16\r\nSouth Korea::15\r\nSpain::Not Rated\r\nSweden::15\r\nTaiwan::R-12\r\nTurkey::15+\r\nUnited Kingdom::15\r\nUnited States::R\r\nUnited Arab Emirates::15+\r\nVietnam::C18',16),(226,'1964418','Tomorrowland','Tomorrowland','Tomorrowland\r\nNesërvendi\r\nDisney Project T\r\nTomorrowland: Um Lugar Onde Nada é Impossível\r\nTomorrowland: Terra do Amanhã\r\nУтреландия\r\nLe monde de demain\r\nTomorrowland: El mundo del mañana\r\nSutrozemlja: Novi svijet\r\nTomorrowland: A World Beyond\r\nTulevikumaa\r\nÀ la poursuite de demain\r\nA World Beyond\r\nProjekt: Neuland\r\nΗ χώρα του αύριο\r\nHolnapolisz\r\nBa\'khazara la\'makhar\r\nTomorrowland - Il mondo di domani\r\nトゥモローランド\r\nRītdienas zeme\r\nRytojaus zeme\r\nTomorrowland: El Mundo del Mañana\r\nProject T\r\nTomorrowland - A World Beyond\r\nDisney Tomorrowland - A World Beyond\r\nKraina jutra\r\nTomorrowland - Terra do Amanhã\r\nTomorrowland: Lumea de dincolo de mâine\r\nЗемля будущего\r\nZemlja budućnosti\r\nKrajina zajtrajška\r\nDežela jutrišnjega dne: svet onkraj\r\n明日世界\r\nYarının Dünyası\r\nЗемля майбутнього: Світ за межами\r\nThế Giới Bí Ẩn\r\n1952',2015,130,6.4,179441,'Eng