y gets ostracized but only an old man stays alone with the idol of the demon. The mistress of the old man do visit the mansion everyday. The house of the family is walking distance away from the mansion which is inhabited by the mistress and her two kids along with the great great grandmother of the old man who is being cursed to live forever after the bite of the demon and the old hag needs to be fed regularly while she is asleep or she might resort to cannibalism.\r\n-\r\nFella_shibby@yahoo.com','Blu-ray',1,1,'',0,'2020-04-25','','2020-04-24 14:17:17','','','','','',0,0,1,'India::A\r\nMexico::B15\r\nUnited Kingdom::18\r\nUnited States::Not Rated\r\nUnited Arab Emirates::18+',18),(227,'3748528','Rogue One: A Star Wars Story','Rogue One: A Star Wars Story','Rogue One\r\nRogue One: Një Rrëfenjë nga Lufta e Yjeve\r\nRogue One: Una historia de Star Wars\r\nRogue One: A Star Wars Story\r\nRogue One: Uma História Star Wars\r\nRogue One: История от Междузвездни войни\r\nRogue One - Une histoire de Star Wars\r\n星球大战外传：侠盗一号\r\nRogue One: Priča iz Ratova Zvijezda\r\nRogue One: Star Wars Story\r\nRogue One: Tähesõdade lugu\r\nRogue One: A Star Wars story\r\nStar Wars: Rogue One\r\nZsivány Egyes: Egy Star Wars-történet\r\nRogue akhat: Sipour Milkhemet ha\'Kokhavim\r\nローグ・ワン　スター・ウォーズ・ストーリー\r\nКүрескер - бір: Жұлдызды соғыстар. Хикаялар\r\nRogue One: Zvaigžņu karu stāsts\r\nŠelmis-1: Žvaigždžių karų istorija\r\nŁotr 1. Gwiezdne wojny - historie\r\nRogue One: Uma História de Star Wars\r\nRogue One: O poveste Star Wars\r\nИзгой-один. Звёздные войны: Истории\r\nOdmetnik-1: Star Wars priča\r\nОдметник-1: Прича из Ратова звезда\r\nDarebák jedna: Star Wars Story\r\nRogue One: Príbeh Star Wars\r\nRogue One: zgodba Vojne zvezd\r\n星際大戰外傳：俠盜一號\r\nRogue One: Bir Star Wars Hikâyesi\r\nБунтар Один. Зоряні війни. Історія\r\nRogue One: Star Wars Ngoại Truyện\r\nStar Wars Anthology: Rogue One',2016,133,7.8,595314,'English','United States','Action\r\nAdventure\r\nSci-Fi','Gareth Edwards','Chris 