ny Stark announces to the World that he\'s Iron Man. He faces many problems in his Life, His Lifesource is Poisoning him, The US Government wants his tech, and someone\'s out to kill Stark. That Someone is Ivan Vanko, Son of Anton Vanko who worked with Tony\'s Father Howard, But Howard then sent Anton to Russia. Ivan trys to kill Tony Stark at a Grand Prix in Monaco but Ivan is then arrested. However Tony\'s Rival Justin Hammer helps Vanko escape from Prison and Hires Vanko to create to Suits similar to Tonys. Tony also assigns his Assistant Pepper Potts as CEO of Stark Industries. It\'s now up to Tony to defeat Ivan and Hammer and to fix his Arc Reactor before he can die.\r\n-\r\nahmetkozan','Blu-ray',1,1,'',0,'2020-06-23','','2020-05-14 04:21:00','','','','','',0,0,0,'Argentina::13\r\nAustralia::M\r\nAustria::10\r\nBrazil::10\r\nCanada::G\r\nDenmark::11\r\nFinland::K-12\r\nFrance::Tous publics\r\nGermany::12\r\nHong Kong::IIA\r\nHungary::12\r\nIndia::UA\r\nIndonesia::17+\r\nIreland::12A\r\nItaly::T\r\nJapan::G\r\nLithuania::N-7\r\nMalaysia::P13\r\nMexico::B\r\nNetherlands::12\r\nNew Zealand::M\r\nNorway::11\r\nPhilippines::G\r\nPoland::12\r\nPortugal::M/12\r\nRussia::12+\r\nSingapore::PG\r\nSouth Africa::13\r\nSouth Korea::12\r\nSpain::12\r\nSweden::11\r\nSwitzerland::12\r\nTaiwan::PG-12\r\nThailand::15\r\nTurkey::13+\r\nUnited Kingdom::12\r\nUnited States::PG-13\r\nUnited Arab Emirates::PG-15\r\nVietnam::C13',12),(305,'1300854','Iron Man 3','Iron Man 3','Iron Man Three\r\nIron Man 3\r\nHomem de Ferro 3\r\nЖелезният човек 3\r\nGang Tie Xia 3\r\nŽelezný Muž 3\r\nRaudmees 3\r\nRkinis kaci 3\r\nΟ Ατσαλένιος Άνθρωπος 3\r\nVasember 3\r\nIron man 3 fauladi rakshak\r\nアイアンマン3\r\nDzelzs Vīrs 3\r\nGeležinis žmogus 3\r\nIron Man: Omul de otel 3\r\nЖелезный человек 3\r\nGvozdeni čovek 3\r\nГвоздени Човек 3\r\nАјрон Мен 3\r\n鋼鐵人3\r\nDemir Adam 3\r\nЗалізна людина 3\r\nCaged Heat\r\nMarvel Iron Man 3\r\nIron man 3\r\nTemir odam 3\r\nNgười Sắt 3',2013,130,7.1,812991,'English','