wn as F-Society, offer Elliot a chance to take his vigilantism to the next level and help them take down E-Corp, the corrupt multi-national financial company that Elliot works for and likes to call Evil Corp, Elliot finds himself at the crossroads. Mr. Robot, who has personal reasons for wanting to take down E-Corp, also reveals that he already has one ally, an even more mysterious, secretive and highly dangerous shadowy hacking group known only as Dark Army. Meanwhile, Elliot\'s childhood and only friend, Angela, who blames E-Corp for the death of their parents, tries to take down E-Corp legally by joining their ranks and trying to dig up evidence of their corruption from the inside. A wild card in this scheme becomes Tyrell Wellick, an unhinged psychopathic E-Corp yuppie, originally from Scandinavia, who has a very unusual relationship with his dominant and ambitious wife Joanna. After many twists and turns, Mr. Robot\'s plan is finally put in motion - with catastrophic (un)intended results. But that\'s just the end of the beginning of the real story.\r\n\r\nMr. Robot follows Elliot, a young programmer who works as a cyber-security engineer by day and as a vigilante hacker by night. Elliot finds himself at a crossroads when the mysterious leader of an underground hacker group recruits him to destroy the firm he is paid to protect. Compelled by his personal beliefs, Elliot struggles to resist the chance to take down the multinational CEOs he believes are running (and ruining) the world. Eventually, he realizes that a global conspiracy does exist, but not the one he expected.\r\n-\r\nahmetkozan\r\n\r\nYoung, anti-social computer programmer Elliot works as a cybersecurity engineer during the day, but at night he is a vigilante hacker. He is recruited by the mysterious leader of an underground group of hackers to join their organization. Elliot\'s task? Help bring down corporate America, including the company he is paid to protect, which presents him with a moral dilemma. Although he works for a corporation, his personal beliefs make it hard to resist the urge to take down the heads of multinational companies that he believes are running -- and ruining -- the world.\r\n-\r\nJwelch5742\r\n\r\nIn the year 2015, an incredibly unstable cyber-security engineer named Elliot is recruited by a shady group of hackers to bring down the most powerful corporation in the history of civilization; meanwhile, a dark project whose purpose could bring about profound implications for society itself nears its completion.\r\n-\r\nchingeeflingee','Blu-ray',1,0,'',0,'2020-06-23','','2020-05-23 17:15:20','','','','','',1,4,0,'Argentina::16\r\nAustralia::M\r\nBrazil::16\r\nCanada::13+\r\nDenmark::15\r\nFinland::K-16\r\nFrance::Tous publics\r\nGermany::18\r\nIndia::16+\r\nIndonesia::16+\r\nIreland::15\r\nItaly::BA\r\nJapan::R15+\r\nMexico::C\r\nNetherlands::12\r\nNew Zealand::R16\r\nNorway::15\r\nPhilippines::18+\r\nPoland::18\r\nRussia::18+\r\nSingapore::R21\r\nSouth Korea::15\r\nSpain::16\r\nSweden::15\r\nTurkey::18+\r\nUnited Kingdom::18\r\nUnited States::TV-MA\r\nUnited Arab Emirates::16',16),(325,'0167404','The Sixth Sense','Sixth Sense','The Sixth Sense\r\nSexto sentido\r\nO Sexto Sentido\r\nШесто чувство\r\nLe sixième sens\r\nEl sexto sentido\r\n第六感\r\nEl Sexto Sentido\r\nŠesto čulo\r\nŠestý smysl\r\nDen sjette sans\r\nKuues meel\r\nDet sjätte sinnet\r\nKuudes aisti\r\nSjätte sinnet\r\nKuudes Aisti\r\nSixième sens\r\nMeekvse Grdznoba\r\nSixth Sense\r\nThe Sixth Sense - Nicht jede Gabe ist ein Segen\r\nΗ έκτη αίσθηση\r\nI ekti aisthisi\r\n鬼眼\r\nHatodik érzék\r\nद सिक्थ सेन्स\r\nHesse sheshom\r\nThe Sixth Sense - Il sesto senso\r\nIl sesto senso\r\nShikkusu sensu\r\nシックス・センス\r\nŠeštasis pojūtis\r\nDen sjette sansen\r\nSzósty zmysł\r\nAl șaselea simț\r\nШестое чувство\r\nШесто чуло\r\nŠiesty zmysel\r\nŠesti čut\r\nEl sisè sentit\r\n靈異第六感\r\nAltıncı his\r\nШосте чуття\r\nOltinchi hissiyot\r\nGiác Quan Thứ Sáu',1999,107,8.1,957943,'English\r\nLatin\r\n