thereal realm of sneaky creatures and eerie mystique. Can Sarah alone save innocent Toby before she loses him forever in Jareth\'s tangled Labyrinth?\r\n-\r\nNick Riganas\r\n\r\nYoung Sarah is left home alone by her parents and she has to babysit her little brother Toby. But the baby keeps crying and Sarah, while telling him a story from one of her books to make him sleep, inadvertently conjures from a fantasy world, the Goblin King Jareth, who steals the child and takes him to his castle in the middle of a labyrinth. Sarah has to rescue him before midnight.\r\n-\r\nFlavio Rizzardi','Blu-ray',1,1,'',0,'2021-12-30','','2020-07-07 07:01:57','','','','','',0,0,0,'Argentina::Atp\r\nAustralia::PG\r\nBrazil::Livre\r\nBulgaria::B\r\nCanada::G\r\nChile::TE\r\nCzechia::U\r\nDenmark::7\r\nFinland::K-8\r\nFrance::Tous publics\r\nHong Kong::I\r\nHungary::KN\r\nIceland::L\r\nIndia::Not Rated\r\nIreland::G\r\nItaly::T\r\nJapan::G\r\nLithuania::V\r\nMalaysia::U\r\nMexico::A\r\nNetherlands::12\r\nNew Zealand::G\r\nNigeria::G\r\nNorway::12\r\nPeru::Apt\r\nPhilippines::G\r\nPortugal::M/6\r\nSaudi Arabia::G\r\nSingapore::PG\r\nSouth Korea::12\r\nSpain::A\r\nSweden::11\r\nTaiwan::PG-12\r\nThailand::G\r\nTurkey::13+\r\nUnited Kingdom::U\r\nUnited States::PG\r\nUkraine::ZA\r\nVietnam::P\r\nWest Germany::12',0),(439,'1183374','Pet','Pet','Pet\r\nEnjaulada\r\nAnimal de Compagnie\r\nPet: Wenn du etwas liebst, dann lass es nicht los\r\nΚτηνώδη ένστικτα\r\nKetrecben\r\nペット　檻の中の乙女\r\nSchronisko\r\nAnimal de companie\r\nПитомец\r\nLjubimac\r\nAnimal de compañía\r\nKafes',2016,94,5.7,16949,'English','Spain\r\nUnited States','Horror\r\nThriller','Carles Torrens','Jeremy Slater','Eva Baltés\r\nSean Gowrie\r\nAaron Kaplan\r\nJesus Ulled Nadal\r\nSean Perrone\r\nNick Phillips\r\nCarles Torrens\r\nSalvador Torrens\r\nKelly Wagner','Zacarías M. de la Riva','Dominic Monaghan\r\nKsenia Solo\r\nJennette McCurdy\r\nDa\'Vone McDonald\r\nNathan Parsons\r\nJanet Song\r\nGary J. Tunnicliffe\r\nDenise Garcia\r