g Edward, and the ferociously handsome Jacob, after her short-term breakup in The Twilight Saga: New Moon (2009). Now, against the backdrop of a brutish killing spree in Seattle and a fierce rivalry between clans, a vengeful and relentless adversary amasses an invincible army of immortals, hell-bent on revenge. Once more, passion demands a sacrifice--and as an honourable but frail pact timidly forms in the name of love--the gallant suitors must set aside their vast differences to defend Bella. Indeed, this is an impossible love triangle; however, in the aftermath of desire, will the mortal enemies accept Bella\'s tough decision?\r\n-\r\nNick Riganas\r\n\r\nBella and Edward have been reunited, but their forbidden relationship is threatened to be torn apart again with an evil vampire still seeking her revenge. And Bella is forced to choose between her true love for Edward or her friendship with Jacob Black as the struggles between vampires and werewolves continues. But there is still another choice for Bella to make, mortality or immortality?\r\n-\r\nMel from the United Kingdom.','Blu-ray',1,1,'',0,'2021-12-30','','2020-08-21 06:24:02','','','','','',0,0,0,'Argentina::13\r\nAustralia::M\r\nAustria::12\r\nBrazil::14\r\nCanada::PG\r\nDenmark::11\r\nFinland::K-13\r\nFrance::Tous publics\r\nGermany::12\r\nGreece::K-12\r\nHong Kong::IIA\r\nIceland::12\r\nIndia::UA\r\nIndonesia::16+\r\nIreland::12A\r\nItaly::T\r\nJapan::G\r\nMalaysia::P13\r\nMexico::B\r\nNetherlands::12\r\nNew Zealand::M\r\nNigeria::PG\r\nNorway::11\r\nPeru::14\r\nPhilippines::PG-13\r\nPoland::12\r\nPortugal::M/12\r\nSaudi Arabia::PG\r\nSingapore::PG13\r\nSouth Korea::12\r\nSpain::12\r\nSweden::11\r\nSwitzerland::12\r\nTaiwan::PG-12\r\nTurkey::13+\r\nUnited Kingdom::12A\r\nUnited States::PG-13\r\nUnited Arab Emirates::16+',12),(376,'1259571','The Twilight Saga: New Moon','Twilight Saga: New Moon','The Twilight Saga: New Moon\r\nMuzgu: Hëna e re\r\nLuna nueva\r\nA Saga Crepúsculo: Lua Nova\r\nLua Nova\r\nЗдр