iend Billy (Rockwell) has some great ideas for the story, but he\'s reluctant to offer input without invitation. A down-on-his-luck actor, Billy pays his rent by running a lucrative dog-napping scam with smooth-talking Hans (Walken). Just when frustrated Marty begins to fear that all of his ideas have dried up, however, Billy shows up with an adorable Shih Zhu swiped from a quick-tempered gangster (Harrelson), and a desperate trip into the desert finds the ideas flowing like drinks at an open bar.\r\n\r\nBoozy writer Marty (Farrell) is a man in search of a screenplay. He has a catchy title but no story to go along with it. Marty has a couple of oddball buddies, Hans (Walken) and Billy (Rockwell), who make a living by kidnapping rich people\'s dogs, then returning them and collecting the reward, and Marty uses the ensuing events of a kidnapping-gone-awry as fodder for his screenplay.','Blu-ray',1,0,'',0,'2021-12-30','','2020-10-13 10:45:36','','','','','',0,0,0,'Argentina::18\r\nAustralia::MA15+\r\nBrazil::16\r\nCanada::13+\r\nChile::18\r\nColombia::12\r\nDenmark::15\r\nFinland::K-16\r\nFrance::Tous publics avec avertissement\r\nGermany::16\r\nHong Kong::III\r\nHungary::16\r\nIndia::UA\r\nIreland::15\r\nItaly::VM14\r\nJapan::R15+\r\nLithuania::N-16\r\nMexico::C\r\nNetherlands::16\r\nNew Zealand::R16\r\nNorway::15\r\nPoland::12\r\nPortugal::M/16\r\nRussia::16+\r\nSingapore::M18\r\nSouth Africa::18\r\nSouth Korea::18\r\nSpain::16\r\nSweden::15\r\nSwitzerland::16\r\nTaiwan::R-18\r\nTurkey::15+\r\nUnited Kingdom::15\r\nUnited States::R\r\nUnited Arab Emirates::15+',12),(457,'0081505','The Shining','Shining','The Shining\r\nEl resplandor\r\nShining\r\nO Iluminado\r\nСиянието\r\nShining: L\'enfant lumière\r\nL\'enfant lumière\r\n闪灵\r\nIsijavanje\r\nOsvícení\r\nZárení\r\nOndskabens hotel\r\nSurmahotell\r\nHiilgus\r\nHohto\r\nThe Shining - hohto\r\nI lampsi\r\nΗ λάμψη\r\n閃靈\r\nRagyogás\r\nद शाइनिंग\r\nDerakhshesh\r\nHa\'Nitzotz\r\nシャイニング\r\nMirdzums\r\nŠvytėjimas\r\nOndskape